import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"person"}}>{`Person`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`a human being.  In the real estate context, Person is the base class of contacts, leads and actions.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`subClassOf:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://schema.org/Person"}}>{`https://schema.org/Person`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Instances of `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://schema.org/Person"}}>{`Person`}</MDXTag>{` commonly appear as values for the following properties:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Action Properties`}<MDXTag name="ul" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`agent`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`object`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`recipient`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`participant`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"schema-real-estate-agent.md"}}>{`RealEstateAgent`}</MDXTag><MDXTag name="ul" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`owner`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`member (team members)`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"schema-real-estate-office.md"}}>{`RealEstateOffice`}</MDXTag><MDXTag name="ul" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`owner`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`employee`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`member`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"examples"}}>{`examples`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-yaml"}}>{`# here are the most common properties seen in the real estate context.
'@context': 'https://yodata.io/yodata/real_estate'
type: Person
# id values should be public URL that unabiguously identifies the subject
# such as a personal website, blog, or social media profile page.
id: http://callinoates.com/
# Context specific identifiers, such as a database identifier in your backend
# should be in the identifier map object with a referenced context or fully expanded URL.
# for example, if your application context is at https://yodata.io/acme/atom-rearranger#
# and database id is 123
identifier:
  'https://yodata.io/acme/atom-rearranger#id': 123
name: Bruce Wayne
givenName: Bruce
familyName: Wayne
jobTitle: Super Hero
# people move, prefer array of PostalAddress
address:
- type: PostalAddress
  streetAddress: 1008 Mountain Drive
  addressLocality: Gotham City
  addressRegion: New Jersey
  postalCode: 10001
# contactPoint is preferred over string value properties (telephone, email, etc..)
contactPoint:
- type: ContactPoint
  name: Callin Oates
  telephone: '719-26-OATES'
# prefer array
image:
- https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1703149496/hall_and_oates_01_400x400.jpg
url:
- https://twitter.com/callinoates?lang=en
- http://callinoates.com/
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":""}}></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
